title: head of state vs. head of government
pid: 86dba0b9-a816-4874-bddf-8b20add34e73
body: |2-
  The jhead of state is a figurehead,
  good for representing the country to others
  and sometimes to the citizenry.
  Kings and queens are heads of state.

  The head of government controls what the government does.
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
